 Lowswimmer 为世界心理健康日和慈善机构 Tiny Changes 分享了受惊兔子的“Head Rolls Off”封面https://www.nme.com/news/music/lowswimmer-covers-frightened-rabbit-head-rolls-off-world-mental-health-day-tiny-changes-3801609?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lowswimmer-封面受惊的兔子头从世界心理健康日的微小变化中滚落Liberty DunworthThu, 10 Oct 2024 15:09:35 +0000 Music NewsNews..ElectronicIndieLet’s Talk – mental healthhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3801609 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lowswimmer 和斯科特·哈奇森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该慈善机构是为了纪念 2018 年去世的乐队主唱斯科特·哈奇森 (Scott Hutchison) 而设立</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lowswimmer-covers-frightened-rabbit-head-rolls-off-world-mental-health-day-tiny-changes-3801609">Lowswimmer 为世界心理健康日和慈善组织 Tiny Changes 分享了受惊兔子的“Head Rolls Off”封面，</a>该文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lowswimmer 和斯科特·哈奇森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison-lowswimmer@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在 2024 年世界心理健康日，Lowswimmer 分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frightened-rabbit">受惊的兔子</a>歌曲《Head Rolls Off》的感人翻唱，以支持<a href="http://www.tinychanges.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tiny Changes 慈善机构</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/frightened-rabbit-scott-hutchison-tribute-blog-friend-interviews-2312552">纪念受惊兔子的斯科特·哈奇森——一个度过黑暗时期的朋友</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scott-hutchisons-family-launch-tiny-changes-mental-health-charity-2484810">Tiny Changes 的成立是为了纪念 Frightened Rabbit 主唱 Scott Hutchison</a> ，他在与抑郁症作斗争后于<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/frightened-rabbit-scott-hutchison-tribute-blog-friend-interviews-2312552">2018 年 5 月结束了自己的生命</a>。该慈善机构是由这位已故音乐家的家人发起的——他的兄弟和受惊的兔子鼓手格兰特、兄弟尼尔和他的父母。</p><p>它的名字灵感来自于 Frightened Rabbit 的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlatans-pay-tribute-scott-hutchison-frightened-rabbit-members-2363317">《Heads Roll Off》</a>中的歌词（“<em>只要我还活着，我就会对地球做出微小的改变</em>”）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiny-changes-charity-frightened-rabbit-scott-hutchison-mental-health-fund-3071085">旨在改善儿童和青少年的心理健康</a>。在其推出时，和记黄埔的家人解释说，他们希望继续“他的艺术和音乐对很多人产生的积极影响”。</p><p>现在，在世界心理健康日之际，Lowswimmer 分享了这首歌曲的翻唱，该歌曲的灵感来源于该慈善机构的名字。这位独立电子艺术家宣布与该组织建立特殊合作伙伴关系。</p><p><a href="https://lowswimmer.bandcamp.com/track/head-rolls-off" target="_blank" rel="noopener">今天（10 月 10 日）在 Bandcamp 独家发售</a>，单曲筹集的所有收益将捐赠给 Tiny Changes。该歌曲将于明天（11日）在各大流媒体平台上线。</p><p> Lowswimmer 在一份新声明中分享道：“能够与如此伟大的事业合作，同时翻唱如此美妙的歌曲，我感到非常荣幸，这首歌曲对我和其他许多人来说意义重大，来自一张令人难以置信的、具有巨大影响力的唱片。” “心理健康是我们所有人都在努力解决的问题——微小的改变对年轻人来说非常有效，可以帮助他们在遇到困难时找到适合他们的解决方案。” </p><figure id="attachment_3801612" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801612" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801612" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Lowswimmer“Head Rolls Off”单幅作品支持微小变化" width="2000" height="2006" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270-800x802.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270-1392x1396.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tiny-Changes@2000x1270-1068x1071.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801612" class="wp-caption-text"> Lowswimmer 的“Head Rolls Off”单幅作品支持 Tiny Changes。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>这首歌曲首先由 Frightened Rabbit 作为他们的第二张专辑“The Midnight Organ Fight”的一部分分享。这首歌展现了在动荡时期的韧性和崛起——这对于 Lowswimmer 和 Tiny Changes 的工作来说都是一个重要的主题。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://lowswimmer.bandcamp.com/track/head-rolls-off" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到《Head Rolls Off》的封面，并<a href="http://www.tinychanges.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里了解有关 Tiny Changes 慈善机构的</a>更多信息。</p><p> ‌通过创立该慈善机构，和记黄埔的家人旨在帮助支持与心理健康作斗争的儿童和年轻人。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiny-changes-charity-frightened-rabbit-scott-hutchison-mental-health-fund-3071085">他们还宣布了 2021 年的一项国家小额赠款计划，称为“微小改变基金”</a> 。根据该组织的官方网站，它“支持高达 10,000 英镑的创新想法”。</p><p>前一年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scott-hutchisons-brother-and-bandmate-grant-reflects-on-a-year-of-their-tiny-changes-mental-health-charity-2673994">Hutchison 的兄弟、Frightened Rabbit 乐队成员 Grant 接受<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了 Tiny Changes 的作品</a>。</p><p> “年轻人需要大量的帮助和关注，这几乎影响到每个人。并非每个年轻人都会遭受心理健康状况不佳的困扰，但我们的方法是一种预防性方法。我们希望为他们提供处理问题的工具和技能，即使他们处于不需要的时候，”他说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3801618" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801618" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801618" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison@2000x1270.jpg" alt="《受惊的兔子》的斯科特·哈奇森 (Scott Hutchison) 于 2018 年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Scott-hutchison@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801618" class="wp-caption-text"> Frightened Rabbit 乐队的 Scott Hutchison 在 2018 年表演。图片来源：Roberto Ricciuti/Redferns/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> “缺乏理解是令我感到惊讶的主要原因。我没有像斯科特那样受苦，也没有像我们将要帮助的许多人那样受苦，如果你没有感受到这些情绪，那么你几乎不可能理解这些情绪——但是，即使你不能完全理解它，也不需要花太多时间去尝试和理解。”</p><p>去年，已故歌手的家人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-book-of-artwork-by-frightened-rabbits-scott-hutchison-announced-3450718">宣布发行一本包含和记艺术作品和插图的书</a>。在此之前，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-scott-hutchison-book-frightened-rabbit-fans-the-work-3098595">首次将这位已故主唱的歌词和艺术作品收集在一起，收录在一本名为《2021 年的<em>工作》</em>的书中，</a> Frightened Rabbit 的幸存成员将其描述为“向 Scott 肆无忌惮的创造力致敬”。</p><p>名为<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-book-of-artwork-by-frightened-rabbits-scott-hutchison-announced-3450718">“生活在色彩中：斯科特·哈奇森的艺术</a></em>”——该项目通过展示主唱的插图、受惊的兔子艺术作品、粉丝草图、他在格拉斯哥艺术学院时的作品以及“介于两者之间的一切”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/music-interviews/make-tiny-changes-frightened-rabbit-and-friends-on-continuing-the-memory-and-genius-of-scott-hutchison-2526840">“我们会永远想念他”——受惊的兔子、他们最亲密的朋友和合作者庆祝斯科特·哈奇森的美丽</a></strong></li></ul><p>“我们一直牢记这一点，尤其是在 The Work 取得意外成功之后，但我始终觉得它应该存在，” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scott-hutchison-book-living-in-colour-interview-grant-dave-sam-fender-3477826">Scott 的兄弟、Frightened Rabbit 鼓手 Grant Hutchison 去年 8 月告诉<em>NME</em></a> 。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-national-matt-berningers-lyric-book-signed-idles-bass-auction-tiny-changes-mental-health-charity-3765392">The National、IDLES</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-national-matt-berningers-lyric-book-signed-idles-bass-auction-tiny-changes-mental-health-charity-3765392">等</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-national-matt-berningers-lyric-book-signed-idles-bass-auction-tiny-changes-mental-health-charity-3765392">成员的纪念品</a>被拍卖，为心理健康慈善机构筹集资金。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-berninger">Matt Berninger</a>捐赠的个人歌词书、来自 IDLES 的 Adam Devonshire 的 Fender American Jazz bass 以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/los-campesinos">Los Campesinos</a>的<a href="https://www.crowdfunder.co.uk/p/los-campesinos-signed-all-hell-test-pressing">“All Hell”试压</a>！ – 这是主唱加雷斯·大卫 (Gareth David) 拥有的副本，标志着乐队首次提供试压版本。</p><h2><strong>有关心理健康的帮助和建议：</strong></h2><ul><li> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/am-i-depressed-how-to-tell-2067753">“我抑郁吗？” – 有关心理健康以及下一步该做什么的帮助和建议</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://www.helpmusicians.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Help Musicians UK – 为音乐家提供全天候心理健康支持和建议</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="http://www.musicsupport.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">音乐支持组织 – 为与酗酒、成瘾或心理健康问题作斗争的音乐家提供帮助和支持</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="http://www.youngminds.org.uk/?gclid=CIuC-9ye69ICFQYo0wodX48KPA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YOUNG MINDS – 年轻人健康和福祉的代言人</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://www.thecalmzone.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CALM——针对年轻人的反对悲惨生活的运动</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://public.eagleapi.io/magpie/time-inc/nme/AUTO/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.time-to-change.org.uk%2F&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Fnews%2Fmusic%2Fdream-state-primrose-path-addiction-mental-health-interview-2560278&amp;vars[ipcTags.contentId]=2560278&amp;vars[magpie_data.ga_id]=18801022.1568737667" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">是时候改变了——让我们结束心理健康歧视</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="http://www.samaritans.org/how-we-can-help-you/contact-us?gclid=CKyDztKf69ICFSIo0wodYjYL5A" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">撒玛利亚人 – 每天 24 小时提供保密支持</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lowswimmer-covers-frightened-rabbit-head-rolls-off-world-mental-health-day-tiny-changes-3801609">Lowswimmer 为世界心理健康日和慈善组织 Tiny Changes 分享了受惊兔子的“Head Rolls Off”封面，</a>该文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Field Day 宣布 2025 年新地点和日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/field-day-announces-new-location-and-date-for-2025-3801601?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=field-day-announces-new-location-以及 2025 年日期Laura MolloyThu, 10 Oct 2024 15:08:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3801601 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>过去四年来，该节日一直在东伦敦的维多利亚公园举办</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/field-day-announces-new-location-and-date-for-2025-3801601">Field Day 宣布 2025 年新地点和日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/field-day">Field Day</a>宣布了 2025 年的新举办地点。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/field-day-2022-review-london-all-points-east-krafwerk-chemical-brothers-3294839">Field Day 2022 回顾：电子音乐的过去、现在和未来</a></strong></li></ul><p>电子音乐节过去四年一直在东伦敦的维多利亚公园举办，是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/all-points-east">All Points East</a>主办的一日活动。</p><p>今天（10 月 10 日），他们宣布 2025 年将搬到布罗克韦尔公园，加入在伦敦南部公园举办的一系列其他节日，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/wide-awake-festival-south-london-caroline-polachek-3450008">Wide Awake</a> 、Cross The Tracks、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/mighty-hoopla-2023-review-years-and-years-kelly-rowland-3451767">Mighty Hoopla</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/city-splash-in-london-tropical-one-dayer-toasts-afro-caribbean-musics-many-threads-3451098">City Splash</a> 。</p><p>他们还宣布了一个新的日期，2025 年野外活动日定于 5 月 24 日星期六举行，作为布罗克韦尔现场银行假日周末活动的一部分。</p><p> Field Day 音乐节总监马克·牛顿 (Mark Newton) 表示，他对新的地点和日期感到“非常兴奋”，他说这“巩固了我们在伦敦夏季伊始的地位”。</p><p>他继续说道：“在与 All Points East 在维多利亚公园合作了四年非常成功之后，2025 年似乎是再次举办我们自己的独立活动的理想时机。新场地和日期的可用性提供了这样做的绝佳机会。” </p><figure id="attachment_3801613" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801613" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801613" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Field-Day-2024.-CREDIT_-Danny-North-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801613" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年野外活动日。图片来源：Danny North</figcaption></figure><p> Field Day <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/field-day-new-location-2018-south-london-brockwell-park-lambeth-2233970">此前于 2018 年在布罗克韦尔公园举行</a>，随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/field-day-2019-live-review-day-1-2506590">于 2019 年短暂移至伦敦北部的 Drumsheds</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/field-day-to-return-to-east-londons-victoria-park-for-2021-edition-2898317">疫情过后，他们于 2021 年返回维多利亚公园</a>，该音乐节在 2018 年之前已在这里举办了 11 年。</p><p>随着 Field Day 移至布罗克韦尔公园，Wide Awake 将从周六的位置移回原来的周五位置，明年的节日将于 5 月 24 日周五举行。</p><p> Brockwell Live 总监马库斯·威登 (Marcus Weedon) 在一份新闻稿中表示：“根据我们目前的《Wide Awake》、《Cross The Tracks》和《City Splash》的名单，我们认为 Field Day 完美地契合了五月银行假日周末，使其成为 2025 年不容错过的日期”。</p><p>今年的 Field Day 中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a>成为头条新闻，同时还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/2manydjs">2ManyDJs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/romy">Romy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mura-masa">Mura Masa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/i-jordan">I. Jordan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yves-tumor">Yves Tumor</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sega-bodega">Sega Bodega</a>的表演。</p><p> 2022 年， <em>NME</em>前往该音乐节，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/field-day-2022-review-london-all-points-east-krafwerk-chemical-brothers-3294839">四星评价</a>中称其为“迄今为止最激动人心的策展”之一，并“回归其最擅长的领域：展示电子音乐的过去、现在和未来”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/field-day-announces-new-location-and-date-for-2025-3801601">Field Day 宣布 2025 年新地点和日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
